13.2 APPENDIX B - SCRIPTS
The following two scripts files are examples and can be created by using Note Pad, and
are used with the PC Test System. They should be included in the TClient release.
13.2.1
Acquire and Send Subset 0 Script
The following script file (Script_NT_Acquire_Send0.txt) should be included in the
TClient release. The script file acquires and sends subset 0, 500 times at 1 second
intervals.
1.
/ Focus Acoustic acquire and send subset 0 script;
2.
/ This script repeats to acquire subset 0;
3.
tooltype(MATRIX_NT);
4.
/ uncomment the following line to reset tool;
5.
/toolcommand(0x00);
6.
/ uncomment the following line to Wait 10 seconds;
7.
/wait(10000);
8.

9.
/ Set loop counter;
10.
10. loopcount(0,500);
11.
repeat;
12.
/ Wait 1.0 seconds;
13.
wait(1000);
14.
/ Acquire and Send subset 0;
15.
toolcommand(0x20);
16.
/ repeat until zero;
17.
if(loopcount(0)) goto repeat;
13.2.2
Send Subset E Script
The following script file (Script_NT_SendE_Mx.txt) should be included in the TClient
release. The script file sends subset E 500 times at 1 second intervals.
1.
/ Focus Acoustic Send subset E script;
2.
/ This script repeats to send subset E;
3.
tooltype(MATRIX_NT);
4.
/ uncomment the following line to Reset tool;
5.
/toolcommand(0x00);
6.
/ uncomment the following line to Wait 10 seconds;
7.
/wait(10000);
8.

9.
/ Set loop counter;
10.
loopcount(0,500);
130972-956 / 2809 XA
